---
title: Family Favourite Chicken, Serrano and Butternut Linguine with Tenderstem® Broccoli and Creme Fraiche
description: Salty Serrano ham pairs with sweet butternut squash and Tenderstem® in a creamy sauce to coat linguine. That's what makes this recipe one of our favourites, and it's sure to be a favourite at your table too.
